---
layout: base
title: Lost in the time stream
description: The page you requested could not be found.
permalink: /404.html
indexed: false
---

{% css %}
.police-box-container {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    inline-size: min(200px, 40vw);
    animation: pulse 2s infinite, in-flight 8s both;

    @media screen and (width <= 1059px) {
        display: none;
    }

    &:is(img,picture) {
        display: block;
        inline-size: 100%;
        block-size: auto;
    }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .police-box-container {
        animation: none;
    }
}
#not-found {
    --band--body--Wrap: nowrap;
    --band--body--Gap--horizontal: 0;
    --card--Width: 60ch;
}
{% endcss %}

{% block masthead %}
    {% include "_masthead.njk" %}
{% endblock %}

<main id="main-content" aria-label="Main content" tabindex="-1">
    <a-band id="not-found" double>
        <h2 class="title highlight" slot="header">Error 404: lost in the time stream</h2>
        <div class="police-box-container accent--orange" aria-hidden="true">
            <img src="../img/police-box.png" alt="" loading="eager">
        </div>
        <a-card bordered style="z-index: 2">
            <div class="content">
                <p>Well... this is awkward. The page you're looking for has wandered into an alternate timeline...or regenerated! Or maybe it never existed in <em class="underline">this</em> universe?</p>
                <p><strong>The good news:</strong> you've got the whole site to explore. <em class="brand">Allons-y!</em></p>
            </div>
            <p slot="footer"><a href="/" class="cta-link">Take me somewhere that exists</a></p>
        </a-card>
    </a-band>
</main>
